events.title: Subpoena Response Package Notification
events.description: TD Ameritrade's secure file transfer service sends a notification to LaTisha R. Hough that a package containing responses to a grand jury subpoena in the case against Jeffrey Epstein is available for access.

keyFacts: A secure file transfer package titled 'USDC SD NY GJS v Jeffrey Epstein Subpoena Responses' was made available on October 2, 2019.
The package was transmitted via TD Ameritrade's Ad-Hoc File Transfer Notification Service, indicating the use of financial institution infrastructure for legal document transfer.
The notification was sent to LaTisha R. Hough, who required credentials to access the subpoena response materials.
The document reference 'USDC SD NY GJS' indicates a Grand Jury Subpoena from the U.S. District Court for the Southern District of New York.
This email serves as evidence of the transmission of legal documents related to the Epstein investigation through secure corporate channels.
